  quest_name: Grave Business
  description: "Used to be good for business\u2014miners, coin, the smell of iron
    and ale. \n\nNow? Just bones walking where they shouldn\u2019t. Bad for trade\u2026
    bad for sleep. I\u2019d handle it myself, but I\u2019ve got a shop to run\u2014and
    knees that won\u2019t listen. \n\nPut them back in the dirt where they belong.
    Do that, and maybe I\u2019ll make it worth your while."
